race.comment: BAVARIAN LADY (5) turned in an eye-catching run over 1890m at Toowoomba last time, ridden back before coming home with a powerful run to finish second. The winkers are removed now and looks a top chance in this. DROP THE PILOT (3) has been in the placings in his past two starts, finishing third over 1600m at Gatton last time out. Leading player on recent runs. SUPER FAIR (8) doesn't boast the best winning strike rate but ran a strong race last time out, finishing third and beaten only 2.25 lengths over 1890m at Toowoomba. Likely improver with top-three prospects. CHANGE THE DEEL (2) is usually thereabouts and looks one for the exotics players.
